ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisEnactment of the LABRADOR INNU SETTLEMENTS REMISSION ORDER, 2003 which provides relief to the Sheshatshiu and Mushuau Innu First Nations, their members and others, living on two Innu Settlements in Labrador, from federal income tax and the federal portion of the Harmonized Sales Tax.
